      <a class = 'query name' href = '/query1'>Roll Up</h5>
      <p>Roll up, also known as drill-up or aggregated operation is a multidimensional 
        OLAP query operation that performs aggre-gation on a cubed dataset. This sample query 
       views the results of each column of separate queries side-by-side, comparing the resulting
       values and selected tables. With the aggregation operation roll up, one can view 
       these results with just one query</p>
