      <a class = 'query-name' href = '/query2'>Drill Down</a>
      <p>A Drill Down is nearly the same function as a Roll Up. Instead
        of going higher in the hierarchy, a Drill Down steps down the
        hierarchy from a summarised level to view the data in a moredetailed level.
        The Query shows gathers all transactions made by anaccount and compares 
        adds them in groups of months, quarter,and the year they were made by 
        comparing the timeid in thetransactions table to the time table
      </p>
    </div>
