      <a class = 'query-name' href = '/query3'>Slice</a>
      <p>A Slice Operation forms a subset of a cubed dataset by specifying a 
        single and specific value from one of the dimensionsof the three dimensional 
        cube and settling with that to create atwo dimensional site of the table.
        This query uses the slice operation to determine the count ofeach transaction 
        characterization type that has occurred in ayear that a user would input. 
        The results give a better outlookon how often each characterization is used for 
        each quarterof the year and would help the database owner determine thefrequency of 
        transactions done in a selected year.
      </p>
